{"tid":2095342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國酒吧重開首日盛況","createTime":"2020-07-05T11:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T13:11:11.000Z","uid":73407,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"35d7e7abb53cebacfa9afb332210ba593978f274","tid":2095342,"uid":73407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDXK1C1UqYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaDXK1C1UqYM&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=55323235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aDXK1C1UqYM</a><br />\n而家只係中午12點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535890-20200705.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535890-20200705.htm&d=yjoviXv3QiMsqLwchXvj3xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=83949316\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535890-20200705.htm&h=17c7e438\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535890-20200705.htm</a><br />\n英國政府進一步放寬限制措施，英格蘭今日起容許酒吧、餐廳及髮廊恢復營業。<br />\n<br />\n民眾在封鎖超過三個月後，終於可以再到酒吧消遣，到廳餐用膳和理髮。<br />\n<br />\n有髮廊凌晨就開門，有酒吧早上六時就營業，迎接放寬限制的「超級星期六」，但傳媒憂慮引發新一輪疫情。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒估計今個周末全英格蘭會消耗850萬公升啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n有民眾歡迎可以重過社交生活，有人則投訴封城時間太長。<br />\n<br />\n警方擔心酒吧重開，醉酒鬧事等不負責任行為重臨，呼籲市民自律。<br />\n<br />\n英國政府表示，民眾仍然要在公眾場所遵守社交距離措施，否則仍有引發新一波疫情的風險。"},{"pid":"3ec9439eb0b96c14beedfe84124b4721d549333e","tid":2095342,"uid":289946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"玩完了。。。實爆過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfa373ea58a44c94fd0680b2a934c48e4ab9355a","tid":2095342,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"未到0 就開<br />\n肯定又大爆過"},{"pid":"c2bff2d191d0d01a9ebdfa51156e